16:03.554 --> 16:04.115
Anyway, go ahead.

16:04.175 --> 16:05.236
I'm sorry.

16:05.256 --> 16:12.284
You know, if you don't mind pausing just for a minute, give me the list of papers.

16:12.924 --> 16:13.665
Okay, go ahead.

